<h1>Notegram</h1>

    <p>
        Notegram is an application for creating and managing notes.
        The application can connect to Google Drive to store and synchronize
        note files created by the user.
    </p>

    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Create notes</li>
        <li>Edit notes</li>
        <li>Save notes to Google Drive</li>
        <li>Synchronize notes between devices</li>
    </ul>

